===Levels 54–77/99: Battlestaves===
Crafting battlestaves offers relatively fast experience and is usually cheaper compared to other methods. However, it requires a lot of capital to buy the supplies needed and can be inconvenient for players with less capital available.

Even though water battlestaves become available at level 54, they are usually fairly expensive due to the low supply of [[water orb]]s. It may be cheaper to cut gems up to level 58 and start with earth battlestaves. Fire and air battlestaves have comparable experience rates to green and blue d'hide bodies, respectively, so choose based on the Grand Exchange prices. Green and blue d'hide bodies require a lot less capital.

Crafting d'hide bodies becomes considerably faster at level 77 and even more so at level 84, but air battlestaves remain as a good cheaper alternative.

